The design is appropriately eye-catching. It may be because I'm not familiar with the student organization, but it might be good to have text somewhere that says "organized by Illini Dancesport" (assuming that's the name of the student organization). That would make it clearer who the organizing body is. It would also be good to include ending times as well starting times for the events. Some bullet points may be helpful, something like no experience necessary, all experience levels welcome, etc.

I think the design is eye catching and depicts the activity appropriately.  It is obvious at first glance that the activity involves dancing.  The only change I might make is to change the color to yellow or white to match the text in the ad.

I think it looks very nice. I like how they use purple on a black back ground. It looks very classy and elegant. I think how you have the TIME/PLACE is very informational, as well as the the location in yellow.
